snippet.title: Gran Turismo Concept: 2002 Tokyo-Seoul (PS2 Gameplay)
snippet.description:
Gran Turismo Concept: 2002 Tokyo-Seoul (PS2) - Car: Honda Mobil 1 NSX JGTC - Course: Tokyo R246

2002 Tokyo-Seoul features cars from the 2001 Tokyo version plus additional models unveiled at the Seoul Motor Show. This game introduced South Korean automakers, like Hyundai, in the Gran Turismo series.
